message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.NE". This is because the paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for summarization and evaluation of news articles, which are common topics in these sub-categories. Specifically, "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) are also likely as they deal with machine learning and information extraction. "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are less likely but still possible sub-categories as they deal with machine learning techniques used in the paper.
